biotools.summary:
NMFNA: a non-negative matrix factorization network analysis method for identifying communities and characteristic genes from pancreatic cancer data.

we have provided demo data and Pancreatic Cancer data for NMFNA, if you want to run NMFNA method, please run the script "Demo.m" directly.
